data.description: Looking for a home with plenty of room for all the toys? Welcome to slide Mountain Loop. This property features a three car garage attached and a 25x50 garage behind the home. The 25x50 has a two 220 outlets, several 110 @ 4ft, footers for a car lift plus 220 in the ceiling. Back up storage, additional 100 amp pane runs the shop. Shop door is a 10x8, and is fully insulated with mini splits. The beautiful home features laminate counter tops, with open layout with fully tiled floors. Primary bedroom features a fully tiled walk in shower and dual sinks in the bathroom. Guest bedroom is perfect comfort for your family visits.
